snippet.title: Kantara Chapter 1 Trailer - Hindi | Rishab Shetty | Rukmini | Vijay Kiragandur | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
From Hombale Films ‚Äî the makers behind KGF: Chapter 1 & 2 and Salaar ‚Äî and the visionary, National Award‚Äìwinning Filmmaker and Actor Rishab Shetty, comes the official trailer for Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1. 

Starring Rishab Shetty as Berme, Rukmini Vasanth as Kanakavathi, and Gulshan Devaiah as Kulashekara, supported by a formidable ensemble cast.With a soul-stirring score by B. Ajaneesh Loknath and produced by Vijay Kiragandur under Hombale Films, Kantara: A Legend ‚Äì Chapter 1 promises visceral action, haunting melodies and a saga that will echo through generations. 

Witness India's Divine Epic on Screens this 2 October 2025.

PRESENTS

BABY by Ujan Shakya || New Newari Song || New Nepal Bhasa Song || New Nepali Song

"Baby" explores the theme of love. It depicts the concept of love at first sight through a narrative that combines imagination and emotion. The piece is characterized as an emotional afrobeat , featuring a blend of Newari instruments.

Tu hai bandi ghalat

mohol badalati hai kaise

Buri aafat tu
Buri aadat tu

Kokaina ina ina ina ina ina ina (mujhe hit karti hai jaise)

Yeh pareshan karegi 
Leke jaan rahegi
Bada nuksaan karegi
Aaj koi kaand karegi

Tu hi hai alpha tu hi hai beta
Galt jo dekhe tujhe
Tujhe tod du gita 
saanvle rang ki nagin jaisi
Hit karti hai jaise chitta

Aaju baaju na koi fatakra 
Launda koi na palk jhapakra
Tar tar tar hai Paseena tapakra
Vo bhi ni hatri mai bhi ni hatra

Sun o Haseena
Kamar ghuma
aane de paseena
Aapka scene me tod na koi
game me apna bhi tod koi na

snippet.title: Tumse Behtar | Varun D, Janhvi K, Sanya M, Rohit S | Tanishk B, Arijit S, Manoj M | SSKTK
snippet.description:
You‚Äôve seen them dance, you‚Äôve seen them fall in love, now witness the heartbreak when love gets intertwined! Presenting ‚ÄòTumse Behtar‚Äô from ‚ÄòSunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari‚Äô, starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra and Rohit Saraf. Composed by Tanishk Bagchi and written by Manoj Muntashir, this beautiful song is sung by Arijit Singh.

#TumseBehtar #ArijitSingh #TanishkBagchi #SSKTK

Music Composer: Tanishk Bagchi
Lyricist: Manoj Muntashir
Singer: Arijit Singh
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi & Krishna Kishor
Woodwinds: Nikhil Ram
Keys: Navneeth, Anoop, Melvin
Male Chorus: Rahul, Sanjay, Abijith, Aston
Female Chorus: Kamalaja, Fathima, Nayansi, Aarthi
Arijit Singh's Vocals Recorded by: Sukanto Singha
Arijit Singh‚Äôs Recordings Managed by: Ashish Biswal
Mixed and Mastered by: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani and Varun Dhawan
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Lyrics:
Tumhara-mera milna likha to hoga kahin
Naseebon ka sitara, mila to hoga Kahin

Na Jane kyun ae humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Raaton me, bina tumhare ghabrayein, ghabraayein
Khwaabon me, milo agar khush ho jaayein ho jaayein

Chain ho tum aaram ho shayad
Koi sukoon ki shaam ho shayad
Khushi kahoon ya dil ki tasalli
Kya tumhein doon main naam

Kitabein dekhi saari, mili na koi shaayri
Tareefein karoon kaise, yahi hai muhskil meri

Na Jane kyun a humnasheen
Hai mere dil ko ye yaqeen
Ki tum sang ho to, bigdi baatein, saari ban jayengi
Tum jo has do, roothi raatein saari man jayengi
Jo daraeyin wo hawayein gham ki, tham jayengi

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Dekho na ye kamaal hua hai
Aesa dil ka haal hua hai
Dil mera tere itar me dooba
Jaise koi roomal hua hai

Aesi hai khwahish dil me mere
Jaane mujhe sab naam se tere
Aesi diwangi pahle nahin thee
Haal ye pichhle saal hua hai

Tumse behtar, tumse pyara yaara koi nahin
Aasmaa pe, tumse roshan, tara koi nahin!

Koi nahin tumse behtar, tumse pyaara
Tumse zyaada mera koi nahin!

Dive into the passionate world of love and longing with the sensational hit 'Ve Kamleya' from the movie Rocky Aur Rani Kii Prem Kahaani. Rendered in the soulful voices of Altamash Faridi, Arijit Singh, Shadab Faridi, and Shreya Ghoshal, this Love Sentimental classic is sure to pull at your heartstrings. Evoking a sense of earnest love and deep emotion, this timeless piece from the 2023ss is a pure treat for all Hindi song lovers.

Artist: Altamash Faridi | Arijit Singh | Shadab Faridi | Shreya Ghoshal

Rendered in the soulful voices of Altamash Faridi, Arijit Singh, Shadab Faridi, and Shreya Ghoshal, this Love Sentimental classic is sure to pull at your heartstrings. Evoking a sense of earnest love and deep emotion, this timeless piece from the 2023ss is a pure treat for all Hindi song lovers.

snippet.title: New Leagues & Battle Modes Explained in Clash of Clans
snippet.description:
In October Update of Clash of Clans Prepare for the massive Split Matchmaking + New League System update, which separates gameplay into a casual Battle Mode (for farming loot with no Trophies earned or lost) and a competitive Ranked Mode (a new seasonal tournament structure that incorporates all 34 Trophy Leagues). This system introduces weekly Trophy resets for lower leagues and monthly resets for the Legend League, along with a League Floor to guarantee a minimum rank based on your Town Hall level, new Hard Mode Modifiers for the highest leagues, and several new achievements to track your progress in this game-changing competitive environment.

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

The Gayatri Mantra is a powerful and ancient chant from Hinduism. It is believed to bring peace, prosperity, and spiritual guidance for those who recite it. The mantra is a prayer to the divine light and wisdom that illuminates our path towards enlightenment. It is traditionally chanted before and after meditation, and is often used during yoga practices. The Gayatri Mantra is considered to be one of the most sacred of all mantras, and is said to have the power to protect and purify the mind, body, and soul.

snippet.title: Meri Zindagi Ke Malik  |  Imaan Beiman  |  Alka Yagnik  |  Udit Narayan Songs  |  Neelam
snippet.description:
Welcome to our special throwback on the journey to the golden era of the 90s featuring Alka Yagnik and Udit Narayan's rare gem ‚Äì Meri Zindagi Ke Malik from the movie Imaan Beiman. Their voices not only defined but exemplified the true meaning of romance in their songs, leaving listeners spellbound and hearts filled with love. Meri Zindagi Ke Malik is a manifestation of the romantic aura of the90ss, captivating listeners in the beautiful melody. 

Meri Zindagi Ke Malik

Let's embark on a beautiful journey with these romantic songs that evoke a thousand emotions, leaving us reminiscing about forgotten love. We invite you to engage with us, leave your comments, and let us know which is your favorite romantic song from the list. Don't forget to like, share, and subscribe if you enjoyed the journey as much as we did curating it for you. 

Let the magic of music from Alka Yagnik and Udit Narayan continue to live on...

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films‚Äô Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story‚Ä¶and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question‚Ä¶do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?
